<http://dx.doi.org/10.5091/plecevo.98847.figure22>
    dc:description "Figure 22. Cyperus pectinatus. A. Habit (x 2 / 3). B. Inflorescence (x 1.5). C. Spikelet (x 3). D. Glume (x 10). E. Flower (x 10). F. Nutlet (x 10). A from Peter 8794; B-D, F from Greenway & Kanuri 12298; E from Richards 24601. Drawn by Juliet Beentje, reproduced with permission from the artist, originally published in Hoenselaar et al. (2010)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/898173" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5091/plecevo.98847.figure23>
    dc:description "Figure 23. Diversity in the genus Cyperus. A. Cyperus cf. cyperoides. B. Cyperus obtusiflorus. C. Cyperus assimilis. All photos taken in the Itremo Massif Protected Area by Fitiavana Rasaminirina." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/898174" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

